OL,5, The family of a four-year-old girl     
OL,6, killed by a speeding driver has said   
OL,7, her death "means something now" as the 
OL,8, sentencing law is tightened.           
OL,10,FViolet-Grace Youens was killed in St   
OL,11,FHelens, Merseyside, in 2017 by a       
OL,12,Fhit-and-run driver who is now out of   
OL,13,Fjail.                                  
OL,15,FDrivers who kill could now face life   
OL,16,Fsentences as part of changes coming    
OL,17,Finto force this week.                  
OL,19,FHer mother Becky Youens, who has fought
OL,20,Ffor the law change, said: "Every day is
OL,21,Ftorture. I miss her so much."          
